window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>From number one </b><b><i>New York Times</i></b><b> best-selling author Lauren Blakely comes the final book in the sexy, emotional and deliciously addictive No Regrets trilogy...with all new narration from Joe Arden and Vanessa Edwin</b></p> <p>It started as one night. It turned into a friendship. Then Harley became my everything.</p> <p>She owns me, heart, mind and body. And for a few brief days, our future seems bright and certain.</p> <p>Until, the past wraps its arms around us in so many terrible ways. Someone I never expected to see again reappears in my life. Trying to keep us apart.</p> <p>Iâ€™ll do anything for her, but the question is - will anything even be enough?</p> <p><i>Every Second With You</i> is the final novel in the No Regrets trilogy and should be enjoyed following <i>The Thrill of It</i>.</p>"; 
